main.java.embl.rieslab.emu.plugin

Interface UIPlugin


  • public interface UIPlugin
    Interface for an EMU plugin. The plugin main class should implement this interface and the jar should contain META-INF/services/main.java.embl.rieslab.emu.plugin.EMUPlugin file containing the package location of the plugin (example: "main.java.myui.myplugin").
    Author:
    Joran Deschamps
